= Parallel Computing
<parallel-computing>
The #emph[parallel computing] is a field where performance and
optimizations are the main goal. It should be preceded by the best
possible optimizations for the sequential version of the code; only
after that the code can be improved by the use of multi-threading,
multi-processing and other techniques.

